{"tid":751270,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"集娛樂休閒﹑學術於一身的最高學府－香港能仁大學","createTime":"2018-07-21T17:04:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-13T15:56:08.000Z","uid":42734,"like":125,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"870aae05ebed3d850ec4cb6f830c893b9f2a863d","tid":751270,"uid":42734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T17:04:48.000Z","msg":"[資料轉載至官方網站]<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">娛樂休閒<br />\n</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><br />\n校舍<br />\n本校擁有兩幢各六層的自置校舍，面積並非很大，但能全面提供所需的教學設備及足夠的活動空間。校舍設有演講廳、 展覽廳、課室、電腦室、語言實驗室、<span style=\"color: red;\">音樂室 (設有鋼琴及卡拉OK)</span> 、芭蕾舞排練室、學生休息室、健身室、乒乓球室、學生活動室及空中花園等。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n即使是享譽國際的香港大學，相信都沒有提供卡拉OK設備予同學作消閒聯誼的用途。而能仁卻是麻雀雖小，五臟倶全。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">設施<br />\n</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n能仁在2016年收生人數僅12人（又稱能仁十二門徒），以一家只有12名學校的來說，雖然不大，但是設施齊備，所以相信一定能提供足夠的活動空間予各同學。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.ny.edu.hk/web/images/program_bac_20152016/theater_new.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ny.edu.hk%2Fweb%2Fimages%2Fprogram_bac_20152016%2Ftheater_new.jpg&h=e07d111b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n相關圖片：演講廳（圖中眾人皆為臨時演員）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">貼地<br />\n</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>能仁學院身處的深水埗及鄰近社區、深切的進入低下階層弱勢社羣中、親身實踐學習得來的知識、分析問題、運用社區資源、發掘居民間的互助和關懷。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n能仁的校舍位處深水埗，而今年新開的社工課程就正好可以享盡如此的地利作為學習的機會。試想像一下，香港其他院校的社工學生，不是位處薄扶林的高山俯視港島，就是坐在馬料水享盡吐露港美景，又或者是身處在繁華的九龍塘上課。他們能感受到﹑聽得見香港低下階層的聲音嗎？不會，他們只會想到他們自己。而能仁的社工學生，則絕對百分百貼地。每一天上學途中所見之眾生相，皆可以為他們在社工路上作充分準備，又或者是為日後失業作準備。"},{"pid":"9dbbdfc536640b9c4057bff98b58ae9835ed0585","tid":751270,"uid":42734,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T17:05:14.000Z","msg":"資料轉載<span style=\"color: red;\">自</span>官方網站<br />\n<br />\n自膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"586bb620147aab325aa4936e66ba7e51053b7fbe","tid":751270,"uid":72608,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T17:17:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好想去能大exchange"},{"pid":"075e1120ac527bdfb23b6cc13e839d1489a6941b","tid":751270,"uid":42734,"like":40,"dislike":0,"score":40,"quote":{"pid":"586bb620147aab325aa4936e66ba7e51053b7fbe","tid":751270,"uid":72608,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T17:17:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好想去能大exchange"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T17:19:04.000Z","msg":"香港非三大轉去能仁好似要爆4，外國學生非劍橋哈佛唔收"},{"pid":"c6291b8ad6e486951d1acb3c6b86ef285e8471c8","tid":751270,"uid":192491,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T17:22:20.000Z","msg":"收生咁撚嚴格, 2016年得12位聖人入到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我都想入呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad0ae3cc7c663e3b8be89bb28503ac077ea4a650","tid":751270,"uid":68540,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T17:24:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f3032e60de88dc6d393d66e1130cbee6d60aab8","tid":751270,"uid":68540,"like":39,"dislike":1,"score":38,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T17:25:22.000Z","msg":"睇到12門徒我真係笑到噴飯"},{"pid":"1cd525aabba647ffbcf111cfbd3ebaa4690084a1","tid":751270,"uid":59826,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T17:25:50.000Z","msg":"又或者是為日後失業作準備<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img 